      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. HURRICANE is a smart dog who led throughout to score last time at this track (29.36), making it three straight wins. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of three starts. The hardest to beat again. 1. CANYA TERRY has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. 2. PRINCESS LASS produced a moderate performance last time when sixth at The Meadows over 525m behind Mepunga Brockie (31.06) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Must be included in calculations.\",\"runners\":[3,1,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
